        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
          <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold text-primary">Why Study in France?</h2>
          <p class="lead">France offers a rich cultural heritage, world-renowned universities, and a high quality of life. With its central location in Europe, diverse academic programs, and opportunities to learn French, it's an excellent destination for international students seeking a top-tier education in a country known for its art, cuisine, and history.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <img src="/user-assets/img/destinations/franceOverview.avif" alt="France Overview" class="img-fluid rounded">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Facts Section -->
  <section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Key Facts about France</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Education System</h5>
              <p class="card-text">France's education system is known for its excellence in various fields, including business, engineering, and the arts. Many French universities have a long history and strong international reputation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Language</h5>
              <p class="card-text">While French is the primary language of instruction, many universities offer programs taught in English, especially at the postgraduate level. Studying in France provides an excellent opportunity to learn or improve your French.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Culture and Lifestyle</h5>
              <p class="card-text">France offers a rich cultural experience with its world-famous cuisine, art, fashion, and historical landmarks. Students can enjoy a high quality of life and easy access to other European countries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Top Universities Section -->
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5">Top Universities in France</h2>
      <div class="row">
