            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">École Polytechnique</h5>
              <p class="card-text">One of France's leading engineering schools, offering world-class education in science and technology.</p>
              <a href="https://www.polytechnique.edu/en" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
